node_3.description: This is arthur burton's plan for Sunday February 09: Wake up and complete the morning routine at 7:00 am., Practice mixology and experiment with new cocktails from 8:00 am to 10:00 am., Visit the local market to pick up fresh ingredients from 10:30 am to 12:00 pm., Have lunch at 12:30 pm., Spend time on bookkeeping and managing bar finances from 1:00 pm to 2:30 pm., Relax and enjoy some personal time, perhaps reading or taking a walk, from 2:30 pm to 3:30 pm., Prepare and have dinner at 4:00 pm., Open The Moonlight Tavern and greet customers at 5:00 pm., Stand at the counter, making cocktails and chatting with customers, from 5:00 pm to 10:00 pm., Close the bar and clean up from 10:00 pm to 11:00 pm., Wind down and relax before bedtime from 11:00 pm to 12:00 am..
